definition: being one more than four, a playing card or a domino or a die whose upward face shows five pips
details:
adjective
- being one more than four
noun
- a playing card or a domino or a die whose upward face shows five pips
= synonyms: five-spot
- a team that plays basketball
= synonyms: basketball team
- the cardinal number that is the sum of four and one
= synonyms: quintet, quintette, fivesome, quintuplet, quint, cinque, pentad
